Four Germany players have been shortlisted for the World Cup Golden Ball award along with Argentina stars Angel Di Maria, Lionel Messi and Javier Mascherano.

Germany's fine World Cup sees defenders Mats Hummels and Philipp Lahm make the list along with Thomas Muller and Toni Kroos.

